<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ح ل أ:</span> يُقَالُ <span class="c2">(حَلَّأَ)</span> السَّوِيقَ <span class="c2">(تَحْلِئَةً)</span> قَالَ الْفَرَّاءُ: قَدْ هَمَزُوا مَا لَيْسَ بِمَهْمُوزٍ لِأَنَّهُ مِنَ الْحَلْوَاءِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>